    <p>Lo­cal tra­di­tional Teochew con­fec­tionery Thye Moh Chan is launch­ing new moon­cake flavours – As­sorted Nuts White Lo­tus and Lychee Rose White Lo­tus ($11.80 a piece, $42.80 for a box of four) – which are cre­ated us­ing sugar-free white lo­tus paste.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Thye Moh Chan’s out­lets at 01-45 Chi­na­town Point, 133 New Bridge Road; B1-12 Paragon,</p>
    <p>290 Or­chard Road; & B2-231 Jewel Changi Air­port, 78 Air­port Boule­vard</p>
    <p>MRT: Chi­na­town/Or­chard/Changi Air­port WHEN: Aug 21 - Sept 16</p>
    <p>INFO: www.thye­mo­hchan.com</p>


